A minimalistic architectural blueprint rendered in soft teal and white tones, showing an exploded isometric view of nested rectangular frames floating in space, each layer slightly offset and casting subtle shadows. The innermost frame contains abstract geometric shapes representing content blocks - columns of varying widths arranged in a grid pattern. The composition suggests modular construction and systematic organization, with clean lines and precise spacing. Thin connecting lines trace pathways between the layered frames, evoking navigation flow. The background is a crisp off-white with a faint grid texture, giving the image a technical yet elegant drafting quality.
